title: frankbitcoin
author: frankbitcoin
content: PSA order has been in 'assembly' for about two weeks now so I imagine I'll have final word on grades here shortly.  I'm expecting 10's but we'll see  If anyone has interest feel free to send me a message and I'll let you know when they are in my hands.I'll have:x2 Ginter #83 X cards (the black regular size)x1 Ginter #83 silver glossyI'll accept reasonable offers that are below ebay listed prices.  Current one listed on ebay for PSA 10 is $6K.  Hit me up if interested.  Will also post pics and update this thread when they arrive.

comments.author: Mrstacy
comments.body: You would think that when at the assembly stage, the item would get to you soon.  The QA checks also take a bit of time.  if they got to you in 4 weeks, i'd be surprised, but congrats none the less.

comments.author: frankbitcoin
comments.body: Quote from: Mrstacy on June 05, 2022, 01:01:51 PMYou would think that when at the assembly stage, the item would get to you soon.  The QA checks also take a bit of time.  if they got to you in 4 weeks, i'd be surprised, but congrats none the less.  yeah, it's been a wild ride with PSA, huh?  my last order took 1 year and 1 month to finally get back to me
